==English==
===Etymology===
From the Greek ''Zephyrus'', (the West Wind)

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛfə(r)|-ɛfə(r)]]

===Noun===
'''zephyr'''
# a light [[refreshing]] [[wind]]; a [[gentle]] [[breeze]]
# any thing of fine, [[soft]], or light quality, especially [[fabric]]

